This paper is about a library for optimizing deep learning performance across frameworks and hardware platforms. It covers a wide range of topics related to deep learning, including neural networks, optimization, and hardware. Therefore, it could fit into several arXiv CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper is primarily focused on improving the performance of deep learning models. Other likely categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), as these areas are also relevant to the paper's content.
